    Note over Client,Zookeeper: System Architecture & Initialization

    rect rgb(230, 240, 250)
    Note over Zookeeper: Initialization Phase
    Zookeeper->>Zookeeper: Start coordination service
    Note over Zookeeper: Listen on port 2181
    end

    rect rgb(220, 240, 230)
    Note over Kafka,Zookeeper: Kafka Startup
    Kafka->>Zookeeper: Register as broker
    Zookeeper-->>Kafka: Registration confirmed
    Kafka->>Kafka: Initialize partitions
    Note over Kafka: Listen on port 9092
    end

    rect rgb(240, 230, 220)
    Note over SchemaRegistry,Kafka: Schema Registry Startup
    SchemaRegistry->>Kafka: Connect to bootstrap servers
    Kafka-->>SchemaRegistry: Connection established
    SchemaRegistry->>SchemaRegistry: Initialize schema store
    Note over SchemaRegistry: Listen on port 8081
    end

    rect rgb(250, 240, 220)
    Note over Client,Kafka: Client Operations
    Client->>Kafka: Produce messages to 'orders' topic
    Client->>Kafka: Consume messages from 'orders' topic
    Client->>SchemaRegistry: Validate message schema (optional)
    SchemaRegistry-->>Client: Schema validation result
    end

    Note over Client,Zookeeper: System ready for message processing
